en widget s tim ID-om.','Widget type (id_base) is required.'=>'Vrsta widgeta (id_base) je obvezna.','The provided widget type (id_base) cannot be updated.'=>'Navedena vrsta widgeta (id_base) ne može se ažurirati.','Cannot set instance on a widget that does not extend WP_Widget.'=>'Nije moguće postaviti instancu na widgetu koja ne proširuje WP_Widget.','Widget type does not support raw instances.'=>'Vrsta widgeta ne podržava sirove instance.','The provided instance is invalid. Must contain raw OR encoded and hash.'=>'Navedena instanca nije valjana. Mora sadržavati sirovo ILI kodirano i hash.','The requested widget is invalid.'=>'Zatraženi widget nije valjan.','The sidebar to return widgets for.'=>'Bočna traka za vraćanje widgeta.','Unique identifier for the widget.'=>'Jedinstveni identifikator za widget.','The type of the widget. Corresponds to ID in widget-types endpoint.'=>'Vrsta widgeta. Odgovara ID-u u krajnjoj točki vrsta widgeta.','The sidebar the widget belongs to.'=>'Bočna traka kojoj widget pripada.','HTML representation of the widget.'=>'HTML prikaz widgeta.','HTML representation of the widget admin form.'=>'HTML prikaz administratorskog obrasca widgeta.','Instance settings of the widget, if supported.'=>'Postavke instance widgeta, ako su podržane.','Base64 encoded representation of the instance settings.'=>'Base64 kodirani prikaz postavki instance.','Cryptographic hash of the instance settings.'=>'Kriptografski hash postavki instance.','Unencoded instance settings, if supported.'=>'Nekodirane postavke instance, ako su podržane.','URL-encoded form data from the widget admin form. Used to update a widget that does not support instance. Write only.'=>'Podaci obrasca kodirani URL-om iz administratorskog obrasca widgeta. Koristi se za ažuriranje widgeta koji ne podržava instancu. Samo za pisanje.','<strong>Error:</strong> The username <strong>%s</strong> is not registered on this site. If you are unsure of your username, try your email address instead.'=>'<stro